        "\n",
        "## Load API Key Securely\n",
        "\n",
        "```python\n",
        "# Colab Secrets (recommended):\n",
        "from google.colab import userdata\n",
        "api_key = userdata.get(\"OPENAI_API_KEY\")   # or GEMINI_API_KEY, etc.\n",
