        "# Build the 3×3 Evaluation Matrix {#sec-eval}\n",
        "\n",
        "For each of the 9 answers, manually fill in the evaluation scores. The schema is:\n",
        "\n",
        "```python\n",
        "eval_records = []\n",
        "for i, row in answers_df.iterrows():\n",
